After realizing the fight was finished, too soon in his opinion, 
Warhead looked around. Inferno was damaged, and Nightshade was nowhere 
to be found. The sphere had not been touched in the battle. it was a 
good thing.

Warhead: Patrol, report damages. Who's good and who's down? (Drillbit 
seemed to be in good shape) Drillbit, come with me and help me drill 
to that sphere.

The rocky crust surrounding the sphere was almost completely gone. 
Soon, they would be able to touch it...
